## Governance & Best Practices

- Order rules most specific â†’ least specific
- Add inline comments explaining why each rule exists
- Optimize for:
  - Auditability
  - Least privilege
  - Separation of duties
- Assume CODEOWNERS will be enforced via branch protection rules
- Do not over-assign security or platform teams to all code

## Output Constraints

- Output only the final CODEOWNERS file content
- Include comments inside the file where helpful
- Do not include explanations outside the file

## Optimization Directive (Important)

Optimize for a future where Muse is used as a reference architecture for
secure, AI-enabled SDLCs in regulated environments.
